Usage
Login:
Visit the login page http://127.0.0.1:5000/login.
Enter your username and password to log in.

Create Short Links:
After logging in, visit the dashboard http://127.0.0.1:5000/dashboard.
Use the "Create Short Link" form to generate short links.

View Analytics:
In the dashboard, you can view the short links you've created and their analytics.

Logout:
Click on the "Logout" button to log out.



Features
User authentication (login and logout).
Short link creation with a 48-hour expiration period.
View analytics for short links created by the user.
Basic error handling and flash messages for user feedback.



Technologies Used
Flask
SQLite (for simplicity; consider using a more robust database in production)
Flask-Login for user authentication
